Package frc.pdp

Class PDP

java.lang.Object
frc.pdp.PDP
public class PDP
extends java.lang.Object
PDP (Power Distribution Panel) contains information about power, current, and voltage for the robot Is cosmetic for now, but should become more useful in the future in diagnosing critical failures
